{"tid":2077984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動post］18/7中大投票師要人！全部同我10/7前登記！","createTime":"2020-06-24T16:37:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T04:03:55.000Z","uid":349692,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"955637a1218edead0c4046f40362990b20572cca","tid":2077984,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:37:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">18/7將會有中大評議會選舉（選一個主席、兩個常務委員）<br />\n10/7前一定要填form登記</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有中大校友都可以報名參加投票</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n填form入呢度：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/agm/eligibility.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fconvocation%2Fagm%2Feligibility.html&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=f0984f6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.alumni.cuhk.edu.hk/convocation/agm/eligibility.html</a><br />\n❗️7月10日登記出席deadline<br />\n- 可以網上填完form簽名直接email去評議會秘書<br />\n- 可以授權比另一個出席者投(獲委任者不可接受多於5位委任)<br />\n❗️7月18日中大評議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n記住收到呢個email先係登記完成！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gymYLzD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgymYLzD.png&h=05800376&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票名單及人選：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pdS87zM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpdS87zM.jpg&h=f5ed92c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有蘋果既報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/H3FF2ILFOP77QH62OCMJ25ETIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2FH3FF2ILFOP77QH62OCMJ25ETIY%2F&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=847b4775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200620%2FH3FF2ILFOP77QH62OCMJ25ETIY%2F&h=e82abc09\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200620/H3FF2ILFOP77QH62OCMJ25ETIY/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">常務委員</span></strong>：一定係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>李軒朗同盧俊宇</strong></span>，兩位係現任民主派區議員（李軒朗係半島連線，盧俊宇係民主黨，贏何妖個個），蘋果有報導對家正動員投另外兩個<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">主席</span></strong>：建議 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">楊于銘</span></strong> <br />\n張秀賢最後關頭雖然想選但未能入闡（文件問題非政治DQ，詳情可以去佢fb睇)<br />\n所以只能係楊于銘同郭碧蓮之間選<br />\n楊于銘之前有張wtsapp圖流出產生爭議（佢竟然同對家郭碧蓮wtsapp仲形容李軒朗係嚟破壞）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW2kYNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW2kYNw.jpg&h=852dea57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但始終係呢兩個候選人間推薦楊于銘：<br />\n- 佢事後承認、道歉同收回言論，形容當時wtsapp對家係想勸退對方<br />\n- 立場上的確唔鮮明，但有手足私底下認識佢係黃，但選舉未有表明立場<br />\n- 張秀賢、李軒朗都有提及係wtsapp圖流出前以為佢係開明派，即係wtsapp事件前佢哋價值觀相差唔太大<br />\n- 就wtsapp內容睇佢有可能反本土派，但佢係評議會已經係現任常委，可能長期制度內以致未能接受制度外參加者<br />\n- 蘋果有報導對家正動員去投現任副主席郭碧蓮，所以佢並非對家之人機會甚高<br />\n楊于銘fb:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kelvin.ymyeung\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkelvin.ymyeung&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPk9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=6368a5fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kelvin.ymyeung</a><br />\n<br />\n總之中大校友們請10/7前登記投票先！到時18/7投邊個可以再諗！"},{"pid":"367e3033d13d541cc44ba77bc623d00cb012ba24","tid":2077984,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73fb490636e6d3feb030c060324a5f5c9888ad3","tid":2077984,"uid":349692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T16:38:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"